{
  "stem": "11067.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, she told them that she would have to take-- bring me a long because I was only seven and a half years old.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what would happen is she would-- they would leave my sister to help my father to cook, and wash, and do all that sort of thing, and help him with the cleaning up there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went with my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was at that point in time that, somehow or other, and that I do not-- I don't know the exact circumstances, that mother found out about Kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she called my father and said, we're sending Suse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father objected, she's not going to be with Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do we know where she's going?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother, plain and simply, sort of said to him, you know, hey, you didn't register us at the embassy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that had been talked about, that my father please go, before Buchenwald already, before Kristallnacht, to register us at the American embassy to get a number, at least, to see if we could get out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, no, I fought for them in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're not going to do anything to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother said, you know, don't be so sure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, of course, here we go again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother, again, the strong lady-- and I've heard of this many times before where the women were the ones that pushed for emigration.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a difficult decision for anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I mean, here were four people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not easy to emigrate to a country where you don't know the language.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
